        "created_at": "2021-09-25T16:41:20.654Z",
        "cooked": "<p>That\u2019s a good question. I tried to run a simulation using <code>lldb</code> and added breakpoints in the <code>runLoop()</code>. From what I can tell, there is indeed only one thread running.</p>\n<p><a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/evan\">@Evan</a>, do you know the reason of using mutex here?</p>",
